---
<footer style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin-top: 96px;">
  <div class="wrap" style="padding-top: 40px; padding-bottom: 48px;">
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 28px;">
      <div>
        <p style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-secondary);">Get in touch</p>
        <a href="mailto:info@momex.io" style="font-size: 20px; font-family: var(--font-display); color: var(--text-primary); text-decoration: none;">info@momex.io</a>
      </div>
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); padding-top: 6px;">
        <a href="/learn">Learn</a>
        <a href="/build-log">Build log</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/MomexApp" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Momex on X" style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
          <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted);">
      Momex is non-custodial. We never hold your keys or your funds.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>